TweetMining - Domenico Solazzo
Version: 0.1 
Note: The library is still in development...
=========================================================================================
Dependencies:
twitter 
Using pypi: pip install twitter

nltk
Using pypi: pip install http://pypi.python.org/packages/source/n/nltk/nltk-2.0.1rc1.tar.gz


=========================================================================================
Data Fixtures:
Add the data fixtures in tests/fixtures.

search.json

You can obtain a search.json using the following url:
http://search.twitter.com/search.json?q=twitter&rpp=5

trends.json
You can obtain a trends.json using the following url:
http://api.twitter.com/1/trends.json

user.json
You can obtain a user.json using the following url:
http://api.twitter.com/1/users/show.json?screen_name=<screen_name>
